OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMost areas
OL,6,Fwill be dry with variable cloud and
OL,7,Fclear spells, with some frost
OL,8,Fpossible, especially in the east. A
OL,9,Ffew showers will persist mainly in the
OL,10,Fwest, while rain continues across far
OL,11,Fnorthern and northwestern Scotland
OL,12,Fthrough the period.
OL,13,
OL,14,CThursday:FMany areas dry with variable
OL,15,Fcloud and sunny intervals, brightest
OL,16,Fnear coasts. Showers in the west and
OL,17,Fnorthwest, with rain and breezy
OL,18,Fconditions across Scotland and
OL,19,FNorthern Ireland. Feeling cool.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
